ard The administration of Gov. Ifeanyi Ugwuanyi of Enugu State, in keeping with its resolve to sustain the tempo of infrastructural development both at the urban and rural areas, yesterday, awarded multiple contracts for infrastructural development across the state, at the sum of over N1 billion. December 22, 2018 In "News" The administration of Gov. Ifeanyi Ugwuanyi of Enugu State has awarded contracts for another set of development projects that are critical to its urban renewal strategy, totaling over N1.4 billion. November 13, 2018 In "News" GOVERNOR Ifeanyi Ugwuanyi of Enugu State, has awarded contract for the construction of the access roads to the 100 Housing Units at Ede-Oballa, Nsukka Local Government Area for workers. October 28, 2018 In "Metro"